sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (Tool)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: TC_088_CSMS: WebSocket Subprotocol negotiation
    Note over CP,CS: OCPP 1.6J

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over CP,CS: Attempt 1 - Unsupported subprotocol only
        CP->>CS: HTTP Upgrade Request
        Note right of CP: Sec-WebSocket-Protocol: ocpp0.1

        CS--xCP: Connection Rejected (no WebSocket upgrade)
        Note over CS: Validation: CS must reject connection<br/>when only unsupported subprotocol offered
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over CP,CS: Attempt 2 - Valid subprotocol included
        CP->>CS: HTTP Upgrade Request
        Note right of CP: Sec-WebSocket-Protocol: ocpp0.1,ocpp1.6

        CS-->>CP: Upgrade to WebSocket Connection
        Note over CS: Validation (Step 4): HTTP upgrade response<br/>must contain Sec-WebSocket-Protocol: ocpp1.6
    end
